WEBVTT

00:00:26.679 --> 00:00:31.056
Kwa mara ya kwanza, tuliweza
husisha muundo wa gari

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:32.841
na mazoea ya ukimya.

00:00:33.824 --> 00:00:35.849
Magari hatimaye yanaweza kuwa kimya:

00:00:36.770 --> 00:00:38.223
amani katika mitaa,

00:00:38.247 --> 00:00:40.659
mapinduzi ya ukimya katika majiji.

00:00:44.762 --> 00:00:51.143
(Hum)

00:00:53.659 --> 00:00:55.826
Lakini unaweza pia kuwa tatizo.

00:00:56.801 --> 00:01:00.779
Ukosefu wa sauti, kwa hakika,
unapokuja katika gari,